metadata.description: HeartBeam, Inc. is a development stage company, which engages in cardiovascular diagnostic technology. Its electrocardiogram (ECG) collection device provides physicians with cardiac diagnostic information for a patient that is outside of a medical institution. The device sends ECG signals to the patient's smartphone and on to a cloud-based software expert system. The company was founded by Branislav Vajdic in 2015 and is headquartered in Santa Clara, CA.
